2012.04.07 0.2.0
+++++++++++++++++++++
1. Added function to set default setting, such as FTP directory, ul/dl speed limit, etc.
2. Added configuration file.
3. Several bug fixes.

2012.04.06 0.1.2a
+++++++++++++++++++++
1. Added function for check database connection (ticket #1).
2. Fixed charset (ticket #2).
3. Added quota set functionality.

2011.06.05 Beta 0.1.1
+++++++++++++++++++++
1. Multilanguage support added.
2. English language added.
3. Installer now in English.
4. Pure-FTPd users table changed (added field 'language').
5. Added interface to create/delete/change Pure-FTPd WebUI administrators accounts.

2011.06.04 Beta 0.1.0
+++++++++++++++++++++
1. Added web based installation. It's create MySQL database, MySQL user for Pure-FTPd WebUI,
Pure-FTPd Users table, Pure-FTPd WebUI users table, Pure-FTPd WebUI config.
2. Some interface changes.
3. Bug fixes.